head in the clouds like you.

846
00:46:21.320 --> 00:46:22.854
Bye.

847
00:46:29.745 --> 00:46:32.071
Is the debt the only issue then?

848
00:46:32.998 --> 00:46:36.728
Mi-joo, listen carefully
to what I'm about to say.

849
00:46:36.752 --> 00:46:39.370
I'll be back.

850
00:46:39.505 --> 00:46:43.943
This used to be your room.

851
00:46:43.967 --> 00:46:45.820
You'll be sleeping here now.

852
00:46:45.844 --> 00:46:48.031
But I don't want to be alone.

853
00:46:48.055 --> 00:46:49.115
No.

854
00:46:49.139 --> 00:46:51.451
You need to learn to be independent.

855
00:46:51.475 --> 00:46:53.676
That's how you become an adult.

856
00:46:54.686 --> 00:46:58.723
I'll teach you one step at a time. Okay?

857
00:46:59.149 --> 00:47:00.850
Okay.

858
00:47:04.404 --> 00:47:06.105
Who is this?

859
00:47:08.033 --> 00:47:09.984
Hello?

860
00:47:23.549 --> 00:47:25.151
Excuse me.

861
00:47:25.175 --> 00:47:26.945
I'm Prosecutor Choi Kang-ho's...

862
00:47:26.969 --> 00:47:30.630
Goodness, you're here. Please come in.

863
00:47:30.931 --> 00:47:32.325
This way.

864
00:47:32.349 --> 00:47:35.176
- Have this.
- Thank you.

865
00:47:38.021 --> 00:47:42.126
On the day you dropped off the side dishes,

866
00:47:42.150 --> 00:47:45.395
Prosecutor Choi came by late at night.

867
00:47:51.201 --> 00:47:52.720
If my mother comes by...

868
00:47:52.744 --> 00:47:56.197
