870
00:47:57.958 --> 00:47:59.626
<i><font color="#ffa07a">To My Mother</font></i>

871
00:48:02.296 --> 00:48:05.164
Are you moving?

872
00:48:05.340 --> 00:48:06.958
No.

873
00:48:07.342 --> 00:48:11.087
But I might have to.

874
00:48:11.805 --> 00:48:16.259
Please give it to her and nobody else.

875
00:48:16.685 --> 00:48:18.496
Please.

876
00:48:18.520 --> 00:48:20.999
But I was off duty that day,

877
00:48:21.023 --> 00:48:23.876
so I didn't even know he'd moved.

878
00:48:23.900 --> 00:48:26.087
Fortunately, you gave me your number last time,

879
00:48:26.111 --> 00:48:28.423
