880
00:48:28.447 --> 00:48:30.273
Sorry it's so late.

881
00:48:33.118 --> 00:48:35.111
<i>To my mother who I miss dearly.</i>

882
00:48:35.203 --> 00:48:37.947
<i>Are you healthy and well?</i>

883
00:48:38.248 --> 00:48:42.368
<i>I got the side dishes you
left at the security office.</i>

884
00:48:43.170 --> 00:48:46.497
<i>I'd always missed your home-cooked meals.</i>

885
00:48:46.798 --> 00:48:50.877
