886
00:48:51.553 --> 00:48:55.158
<i>I'm sorry that my work keeps me...</i>

887
00:48:55.182 --> 00:48:58.760
<i>from calling or visiting you often.</i>

888
00:48:59.436 --> 00:49:01.262
<i>But Mother,</i>

889
00:49:01.355 --> 00:49:03.514
<i>I want you to know this.</i>

890
00:49:04.232 --> 00:49:07.003
<i>We may be apart,</i>

891
00:49:07.027 --> 00:49:09.672
<i>but I still live...</i>

892
00:49:09.696 --> 00:49:14.359
<i>in the memories I shared with you and Father.</i>

893
00:49:14.701 --> 00:49:18.806
<i>I'll see you next week on your birthday.</i>

894
00:49:18.830 --> 00:49:22.992
"September 7. From your beloved son, Kang-ho."

895
00:49:24.086 --> 00:49:25.772
"Kang-ho"?

896
00:49:25.796 --> 00:49:28.373
Did I write this?

897
00:49:29.049 --> 00:49:31.459
It's just so odd.

898
00:49:31.843 --> 00:49:36.881
You've never spoken to me in this manner before.

899
00:49:37.182 --> 00:49:40.161
Why did you leave this with the security guard?

900
00:49:40.185 --> 00:49:44.097
How did you know I'd be
packing your stuff without you?

901
00:49:46.108 --> 00:49:47.585
Tell me.

902
00:49:47.609 --> 00:49:52.256
Did you know you'd end up this way?

903
00:49:52.280 --> 00:49:57.110
