00:50:13.301 --> 00:50:15.387
<i><font color="#ffa07a">Investigation Officer</font></i>

911
00:50:16.596 --> 00:50:17.740
Hello?

912
00:50:17.764 --> 00:50:20.618
It's me, ma'am. You called.

913
00:50:20.642 --> 00:50:22.829
I was attending a trial earlier.

914
00:50:22.853 --> 00:50:25.748
I see. One minute.

915
00:50:25.772 --> 00:50:29.252
Fill it out, and when they call number 25,

916
00:50:29.276 --> 00:50:32.755
go hand them the bank book and the seal.

917
00:50:32.779 --> 00:50:34.215
What's the password again?

918
00:50:34.239 --> 00:50:35.758
The password is...

919
00:50:35.782 --> 00:50:37.900
zero, nine...

920
00:50:38.201 --> 00:50:40.555
Zero, nine, zero, seven. My birthday.

921
00:50:40.579 --> 00:50:42.613
That's right.

922
00:50:43.039 --> 00:50:44.782
I'm sorry.

923
00:50:45.125 --> 00:50:47.869
Assemblyman Oh Tae-soo?

924
00:50:49.004 --> 00:50:51.247
Do you mean...

925
00:50:51.298 --> 00:50:55.528
the assemblyman who's running for President?

926
00:50:55.552 --> 00:50:57.029
The former prosecutor?

927
00:50:57.053 --> 00:50:58.239
<i>Correct.</i>

928
00:50:58.263 --> 00:51:03.384
Prosecutor Choi was engaged to his daughter.

929
00:51:03.435 --> 00:51:04.579
You didn't know?

930
00:51:04.603 --> 00:51:06.345
Goodness.

931
00:51:06.730 --> 00:51:08.681
How could this be?

932
00:51:10.275 --> 00:51:12.003
That's a relief.

933
00:51:12.027 --> 00:51:15.131
I've been acquainted with Assembly Oh.

934
00:51:15.155 --> 00:51:17.633
Could you give me his number please?

935
00:51:17.657 --> 00:51:18.593
<i>Sorry?</i>

936
