943
00:51:36.927 --> 00:51:39.447
And she's getting married soon.

944
00:51:39.471 --> 00:51:42.298
<i>I think it'd be best if you didn't call them.</i>

945
00:51:42.349 --> 00:51:44.967
Here comes the bride.

946
00:51:50.357 --> 00:51:52.460
