Or is something fancier better?

960
00:52:41.366 --> 00:52:43.553
You already look pretty enough.

961
00:52:43.577 --> 00:52:44.762
Whatever.

962
00:52:44.786 --> 00:52:46.931
You do. Let's go.

963
00:52:46.955 --> 00:52:48.823
Kang-ho.

964
00:52:49.374 --> 00:52:53.729
We're visiting your mother tomorrow.
Do you really have to go out tonight?

965
00:52:53.753 --> 00:52:55.481
It's work-related. I won't be long.

966
00:52:55.505 --> 00:52:57.316
You're such a workaholic.

967
00:52:57.340 --> 00:52:59.875
Let's stop by the department store.

968
00:53:02.888 --> 00:53:05.381
<i>We need to make a move first.</i>

969
00:53:05.432 --> 00:53:07.967
I heard about your daughter's wedding.

970
00:53:08.518 --> 00:53:11.497
You'll become in-laws with Dosang Group.

971
00:53:11.521 --> 00:53:13.749
Yes, that's right.

972
00:53:13.773 --> 00:53:16.168
What can I do? Our children are in love.

973
00:53:16.192 --> 00:53:17.295
<i>I understand.</i>

974
00:53:17.319 --> 00:53:19.797
<i>Parents are always bound
to give in to their children.</i>

975
00:53:19.821 --> 00:53:21.841
Though there are parents who kill them.

976
00:53:21.865 --> 00:53:23.509
Mr. Song!

977
00:53:23.533 --> 00:53:25.553
Gosh, you startled me.

978
00:53:25.577 --> 00:53:27.430
<i>It's about time you dropped it.</i>

979
00:53:27.454 --> 00:53:28.973
It's all in the past.

980
00:53:28.997 --> 00:53:30.948
I believe...

981
00:53:30.999 --> 00:53:35.995
