982
00:53:39.966 --> 00:53:43.044
Do you mean the original
copy of the DNA test result?

983
00:53:43.094 --> 00:53:47.632
As you said, it's just a piece of paper.

984
00:53:47.933 --> 00:53:51.412
<i>What if I claim you colluded
with Bareun Hanguk Party,</i>

985
00:53:51.436 --> 00:53:53.414
and fabricated it to take me down?

986
00:53:53.438 --> 00:53:56.265
Then how will you prove its authenticity?

987
00:53:56.483 --> 00:53:59.629
So why did you have to take it so far...

988
00:53:59.653 --> 00:54:02.590
as to kill the poor woman and her child?

989
00:54:02.614 --> 00:54:03.799
What did you say?

990
00:54:03.823 --> 00:54:06.385
<i>I hope we never see each other again.</i>

991
00:54:06.409 --> 00:54:08.235
<i>Goodbye then.</i>

992
00:54:13.500 --> 00:54:15.326
Right.

993
00:54:15.377 --> 00:54:18.204
I expected nothing less from him.

994
00:54:27.555 --> 00:54:28.991
How did it go?

995
00:54:29.015 --> 00:54:31.634
We finally located the file.

996
00:54:36.606 --> 00:54:37.750
In two days,

997
00:54:37.774 --> 00:54:42.019
Oh Tae-soo will become
in-laws with Dosang Group.

998
00:54:42.362 --> 00:54:45.132
And you just managed to locate it?

999
00:54:45.156 --> 00:54:47.843
- Are you kidding me right...?
- Choi Kang-ho...

1000
00:54:47.867 --> 00:54:49.902
is walking again.

1001
00:54:52.956 --> 00:54:54.907
What do you mean?

1002
00:55:02.632 --> 00:55:06.278
See? What did I tell you?

1003
00:55:06.302 --> 00:55:09.004
I told you he'd walk again.

1004
00:55:09.139 --> 00:55:11.826
Where should you record
the pig feed you purchased?

1005
