Well done.

1014
00:55:26.114 --> 00:55:28.607
You're so smart.

1015
00:55:28.992 --> 00:55:32.847
You need to check and
record them every day, okay?

1016
00:55:32.871 --> 00:55:34.613
Okay.

1017
00:55:34.789 --> 00:55:36.642
What am I learning tomorrow?

1018
