<i><font color="#ffa07a">Copied Documents</font></i>

1020
00:55:40.128 --> 00:55:43.831
- Are these all mine?
- Yes, they're all yours.

1021
00:55:45.717 --> 00:55:47.570
Mom, this too?

1022
00:55:47.594 --> 00:55:49.363
Yes.

1023
00:55:49.387 --> 00:55:50.948
Awesome.

1024
00:55:50.972 --> 00:55:53.841
I'm going to show it to Seo-jin and Ye-jin.

1025
00:55:54.100 --> 00:55:56.010
Found it.

1026
00:56:00.690 --> 00:56:02.376
Mr. Kang-ho!

1027
00:56:02.400 --> 00:56:05.227
Hello, you cuties.

1028
00:56:05.487 --> 00:56:08.049
You must be here to hang out with Uncle Kang-ho.

1029
00:56:08.073 --> 00:56:11.052
