1030
00:56:11.076 --> 00:56:12.428
It's okay.

1031
00:56:12.452 --> 00:56:15.765
Ye-jin only came to
congratulate him on walking again.

1032
00:56:15.789 --> 00:56:17.725
She brought a flower.

1033
00:56:17.749 --> 00:56:20.201
Go on.

1034
00:56:20.585 --> 00:56:24.872
They said yellow was your lucky color.

1035
00:56:28.968 --> 00:56:31.378
Thanks, Ye-jin. It's so pretty.

1036
00:56:31.846 --> 00:56:34.673
But of course you're prettier.

1037
00:56:49.280 --> 00:56:51.106
We'll be back.

1038
00:56:53.493 --> 00:56:58.140
I'm going to beat up anyone
who tells me to wash my hands.

1039
00:56:58.164 --> 00:57:00.518
Did you see how we were wearing matching colors?

1040
00:57:00.542 --> 00:57:01.977
This is fate.

1041
00:57:02.001 --> 00:57:04.745
