1052
00:57:41.249 --> 00:57:43.310
"Condolences"?

1053
00:57:43.334 --> 00:57:44.910
Yes.

1054
00:57:46.171 --> 00:57:48.289
Okay, ma'am.

1055
00:57:48.339 --> 00:57:50.207
One minute please.

1056
00:58:06.483 --> 00:58:09.059
All right. Let's try it again.

1057
00:58:10.862 --> 00:58:12.688
Mom.

1058
00:58:13.031 --> 00:58:14.633
